hristian-frattima/" rel="tag">Christian Frattima</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/davide-amadei/" rel="tag">Davide Amadei</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/elina-shimkus/" rel="tag">Elina Shimkus</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/graziano-schiavone/" rel="tag">Graziano Schiavone</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marco-berrini/" rel="tag">Marco Berrini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/nevio-cavina/" rel="tag">Nevio Cavina</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/orchestra-coin-du-roi/" rel="tag">Orchestra Coin du Roi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/valeria-girardello/" rel="tag">Valeria Girardello</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/vilija-mikstaite/" rel="tag">Vilija Miktait</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alessandro Giangrande, Alessio Pizzech, Ars Cantica Choir, Christian Frattima, Davide Amadei, Elina Shimkus, Graziano Schiavone, Marco Berrini, Nevio Cavina, Orchestra Coin du Roi, Valeria Girardello, Vilija Miktait"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block 